FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776409519
OL,3,CMajor seafront hotel to no longer
OL,4,Chouse asylum seekers
OL,6,FHe said: "I am proud to say that after
OL,7,Ftwo years of relentless campaigning
OL,8,Fthe government has listened. The
OL,9,FMetropole Hotel will cease operating
OL,10,Fas asylum accommodation before the end
OL,11,Fof July.
OL,13,F"This is welcome news for our town,
OL,14,Fespecially after the previous
OL,15,FConservative government broke its
OL,16,Fpromise that the hotel would only be
OL,17,Fused for three months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776409519
OL,3,CMajor seafront hotel to no longer
OL,4,Chouse asylum seekers
OL,6,F"I have been clear since it opened in
OL,7,F2021 ` the Metropole should never have
OL,8,Fbeen used in this way. It has placed
OL,9,Funacceptable pressure on local
OL,10,Fservices, damaged confidence in our
OL,11,Ftown, and left vulnerable people in
OL,12,Funsuitable accommodation.
OL,14,F"The Metropole is a historic part of
OL,15,Four identity and a cornerstone of our
OL,16,Ftourism heritage. Like the thousands
OL,17,Fwho backed my campaign, I want to see
OL,18,Fit restored to its rightful role `
OL,19,Fsupporting jobs, attracting visitors,
OL,20,Fand driving the regeneration our town
OL,21,Fdeserves."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
